sub_title: Medical doctor at Praktijk Dr. Sukrisno
summary:
To give an alternatieve treatment for a lot of patients that can not be cured by the western medicine, by means of acupuncture and chinese electroacupuncture (acupuncture with electrostimulation) together with chinese herbs. People with migraine, allergic disorder like hay fever or patient with chronic inflamation of the intestine (like Crohn disease and Colitis Ulcerose) or fibromyalgia (polymyalgia) or rheumatism are not easy to treat with only the western medicine alone. Combination with acupuncture and chinese herbs shows good effect to treat these all diorders. Also post menopausal problems, like hot flushes, high blood pressure and sleeping problems can be treated by acupuncture and chines herbs.

Specialties: Public Health
Acupuncture and Chinese Herbs
